---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - OurCouple" description="OurCouple Privacy Policy: Your data is encrypted. We can't read your messages, photos, or notes. No ads, no data selling, no third-party sharing." canonicalPath="/privacy">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-gradient-radial">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="OurCouple" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl" />
        <span class="font-sans font-bold text-xl text-text">OurCouple</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="flex-1 pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">Last updated: January 21, 2026</p>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Your Privacy Matters</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple is built with privacy at its core. Your content is encrypted, which means <strong>only you and your partner can see it</strong>. Not even we can read your messages, photos, or notes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            This policy applies to our website, waitlist, and mobile application.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">What We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-text mb-3 mt-6">Account Information</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Display name</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-text mb-3 mt-6">Your Content (Encrypted)</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Daily manifestations (messages and photos)</li>
            <li>Inspiration vault quotes</li>
            <li>Shared moments and memories</li>
            <li>Shared notes</li>
            <li>Events and dates</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-text mb-3 mt-6">Waitlist</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Email address only</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Encryption</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            All your personal content is encrypted on your device before being sent to our servers. Only you and your partner have the keys to decrypt it.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            This means:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Your messages, photos, notes are encrypted locally</li>
            <li>Only encrypted data is stored on our servers</li>
            <li>Only you and your partner can decrypt your content</li>
            <li><strong>We cannot read your content</strong> ‚Äî even if we wanted to</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-4 mt-4">
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
              <strong class="text-text">Important:</strong> Because we can't decrypt your data, if you lose your password and can't recover your account, your content cannot be recovered.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Provide and maintain the app</li>
            <li>Sync your data between your devices</li>
            <li>Share your content with your connected partner</li>
            <li>Send push notifications (with your permission)</li>
            <li>Notify you about product updates (waitlist)</li>
            <li>Respond to support requests</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">What We Don't Do</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>We don't read your content (we can't)</li>
            <li>We don't sell your data</li>
            <li>We don't show you ads</li>
            <li>We don't share your data with third parties for marketing</li>
            <li>We don't use your content for AI training or analytics</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Partner Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple is designed for couples. When you connect with a partner, your shared content becomes visible to them:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Daily manifestations</li>
            <li>Inspiration vault quotes</li>
            <li>Shared moments and notes</li>
            <li>Events and dates</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            By inviting or accepting a partner, you consent to sharing this content with them. You can disconnect at any time in the app settings.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li>Access and export your data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
            <li>Delete your account and all your data</li>
            <li>Unsubscribe from emails at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-4">
            Contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@vynse.dev" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark">contact@vynse.dev</a> to exercise these rights. We'll respond within 30 days.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Data Retention</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-secondary space-y-2 ml-4">
            <li><strong>Active accounts:</strong> data is kept as long as your account is active</li>
            <li><strong>Deleted accounts:</strong> all data is permanently deleted within 30 days</li>
            <li><strong>Waitlist:</strong> email is kept until you unsubscribe or the app launches</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Age Requirement</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            OurCouple is for users 16 years and older. We do not knowingly collect data from anyone under 16.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            We may update this policy from time to time. We'll notify you of significant changes via email or in-app notification.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-10">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">
            Questions about this Privacy Policy? Contact us:
          </p>
          <p class="text-primary font-medium">
            <a href="mailto:contact@vynse.dev">contact@vynse.dev</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
        <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark transition-colors font-medium">
          ‚Üê Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-card border-t border-border py-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-text-light text-sm">
        ¬© 2026 OurCouple. Made with üíï
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
